data.title: Dr William Shillinglaw Hewat (1834
data.meta_description: William Shillinglaw Hewat was the first child born to Helen Mary Cunningham and William Hewat, who married at Kelso in Roxburghshire on 11 March 1834.  William's mother, Helen, died at Guelph on 21 September 1848, but her place of interment has not yet been identified.
